item.title: CVE-2022-36894|2024-08-03T10:14:29.353Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20clif%20performance%20testing%20plugin
item.description: An arbitrary file write vulnerability in Jenkins CLIF Performance Testing Plugin 64.vc0d66de1dfb_f and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to create or replace arbitrary files on the Jenkins controller file system with attacker-specified content.
